subject: link to CouchSurfing new privacy policy is a broken link?
text:
according to http://www.couchsurfing.org/terms.html
this is the URL where the privacy policy should be:
http://www.couchsurfing.org/new_privacy.html
but it's not there.

there is probably a story behind this, did they cancel the policy
update after the public protest? does anybody know more about this?
please reply to this thread if you do.

i'll try to do some forensics on this using the internet archive
(wayback machine).
